{"tid":1614296,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［遍地開花］齊齊來做分鐘人 要向美國獨立戰爭學習！","createTime":"2019-10-02T17:44:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T00:34:22.000Z","uid":218570,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f9f7cfb5d28019fbd1b802204a1188fb36c66ec7","tid":1614296,"uid":218570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:44:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">今日證明大家幾嬲都會返工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過一放工就即刻歸位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於今晚快閃加上近屋企 損失較少<br />\n啟發左我地要將抗爭生活化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n目標:極短時間內加入抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n未必要每次full gear(搞到全民帶就最好)<br />\n最低消費口罩手套 日日都帶得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今日開始 全民分鐘人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n分鐘人（Minuteman），也有譯作快捷民兵，是指美國獨立戰爭時期麻省的一類召之即來的特殊民兵組織。其成員從美國各地民兵中挑選出特別精壯的成員所集結。<br />\n<br />\n顧名思義，分鐘人具有高機動性、快速部署的能力，<span style=\"color: red;\">一旦有狀況發生，可以在一分鐘內就集合趕到現場</span>，使到殖民地能夠迅速對戰鬥進行應對。<br />\n<br />\n他們是第一批參加美國獨立戰爭的組織之一，成員佔了整個民兵組織的1/4。大部分成員都比較年輕，也比較具有機動性，成為了早期革命響應者網路的一部份。 <br />\n<br />\nFrom wiki"},{"pid":"8bad1e2f30c40b0e352954bb5b9085ded4d11b4c","tid":1614296,"uid":218570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:44:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我們都是分鐘人</span></span>"},{"pid":"c4ee4c9a78f2c3f423ff42515334c614674dc48d","tid":1614296,"uid":172465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:45:37.000Z","msg":"已經做咗兩個月了"},{"pid":"d8eb106158f8a566630cb700260a1821a66d028d","tid":1614296,"uid":303052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:46:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Mtqwir.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail